### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users

### Get all users with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?city=Mumbai&minAge=20&maxAge=30

### Get all users with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?page=1&limit=2

### Get single user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/1

### Create new user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Priya",
  "email": "priya@example.com",
  "age": 24,
  "city": "Bangalore"
}

### PATCH - Update only age (partial update)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "age": 27
}

### PATCH - Update only city (partial update)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Chennai"
}

### PATCH - Update multiple fields (partial update)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Johnson",
  "age": 28
}

### PUT - Full replacement (all fields required)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob Smith",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "age": 32,
  "city": "Delhi"
}

### PUT - Missing fields (will set to null)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "email": "bob@example.com"
}

